Salud!

36:53.960 --> 36:55.920
Whoo!
Oh, shit!

36:55.920 --> 36:57.680
Whoo!

36:57.680 --> 37:00.000
What's up? What's wrong?
Tracy's...birthday.

37:00.000 --> 37:01.920
Oh.
Forgot to call her!

37:01.920 --> 37:04.840
Oh. (LAUGHS)
No, don't fuckin' laugh.

37:06.000 --> 37:08.520
Do you have a phone I could use?
Tres pesos.

37:08.520 --> 37:10.280
I need to make a call.

37:10.280 --> 37:12.840
Telephone? Telephone?

37:14.920 --> 37:16.120
Thank you.

37:29.120 --> 37:31.280
Hola, chica!

37:31.280 --> 37:34.280
Hello, sirs. Having fun?

37:34.280 --> 37:36.480
Do you boys like to party?

37:37.800 --> 37:39.520
Yeah, we do.

37:42.200 --> 37:43.640
Uh-oh.

37:44.960 --> 37:45.960
Si.

37:45.960 --> 37:47.680
Gracias.

37:47.680 --> 37:49.200
Si, chica, gracias.

37:49.200 --> 37:53.200
Hey, have some fun, OK? It's Mexico.

37:53.200 --> 37:55.560
What?

38:26.640 --> 38:28.320
MAN: Sit down.

38:57.920 --> 38:59.280
Uh...

39:00.280 --> 39:01.840
This isn't the number
I discussed with Xander.

39:01.840 --> 39:06.120
You want the money,
we need the product, yeah?

39:40.120 --> 39:42.200
Well, you can see yourself out.

39:55.040 --> 39:56.800
Hey, hey, hey, hey.

39:57.800 --> 39:59.800
Careful of needles.

40:22.200 --> 40:24.440
(GRUNTS)

40:24.440 --> 40:26.040
(GROANS)

40:28.080 --> 40:29.400
(GRUNTS)

40:29.400 --> 40:30.920
(GROANS)

40:31.920 --> 40:34.800
(GRUNTS)

40:34.800 --> 40:38.440
(MOANS)

40:38.440 --> 40:41.520
No, no, no, no, no, no.

40:45.080 --> 40:46.280
(GRUNTS)

40:47.280 --> 40:49.640
(GROANS)

40:49.640 --> 40:53.720
(OTHERS LAUGH)

41:02.360 --> 41:04.760
Starting early, Miss?

41:04.760 --> 41:08.280
Something like that.
Don't drink it all yourself.

41:15.480 --> 41:16.640
It's money.

41:16.640 --> 41:19.600
For you. Not for that business.

41:19.600 --> 41:21.760
Thanks, Dad.

41:22.880 --> 41:27.280
So, uh...where is he, anyway?
Doesn't he know it's your birthday?

41:27.280 --> 41:30.880
My husband is overseas on business.

41:35.800 --> 41:39.520
Trot's in the US finalising
a very big deal for Lightwave.

41:39.520 --> 41:42.560
Reckon that's a very good reason
to miss my birthday dinner.

41:56.720 --> 41:59.360
TROTTER: You know, yeah?
HUNTER: I do, I do.

41:59.360 --> 42:00.960
Oh. Uh...

42:00.960 --> 42:03.240
I'm... I'm sorry, I'm taken.

42:03.240 --> 42:05.000
(CHUCKLES) I'm married.

42:05.000 --> 42:06.720
Not available.

42:06.720 --> 42:09.600
Not... (CHUCKLES) Not available.

42:09.600 --> 42:11.480
Hey, how long's he gonna be?
I'm only human, man.

42:11.480 --> 42:13.320
I'm gonna go check on him.

42:13.320 --> 42:16.280
Uh... Tell him to hurry up.

42:16.280 --> 42:18.120
No, sorry. Married.

42:19.240 --> 42:20.880
Hola, gato.

42:22.320 --> 42:25.640
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)

42:28.400 --> 42:30.360
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)

42:30.360 --> 42:31.920
(BANGS)

42:31.920 --> 42:33.280
Buddy!

42:33.280 --> 42:34.600
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)

42:34.600 --> 42:37.040
Come on, man, let's wrap it up!
(BANGS)

42:37.040 --> 42:38.760
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)

42:38.760 --> 42:39.760
Buddy.

42:39.760 --> 42:42.960
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)

42:42.960 --> 42:43.960
Buddy!

42:43.960 --> 42:46.000
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH, CRIES)

42:46.000 --> 42:47.840
No, no, no, no, no!

42:47.840 --> 42:49.920
No. Oh, my God, wake up.

42:49.920 --> 42:51.840
(SHOUTS) No, don't fuckin' do this!

42:51.840 --> 42:53.440
(WOMAN SPEAKS IN SPANISH)
No, come on, wake up!

42:53.440 --> 42:54.800
Wake up. Wake up.

42:54.800 --> 42:56.280
That's it!
I'm here, I'm here, I'm here!

42:56.280 --> 42:57.920
Hey, man. What's up?
Hey. Hey, hey, hey, hey.

42:57.920 --> 43:00.280
Hey. Hey! Listen to me,
you get it together right now.

43:00.280 --> 43:02.720
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)
Right now. Listen to me, OK?

43:02.720 --> 43:03.720
Que pedo?!

43:03.720 --> 43:05.480
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)

43:05.480 --> 43:06.960
(SPEAKS IN SPANISH)

43:06.960 --> 43:09.040
I can explain. I know how it looks...
(SPEAKS IN SPANISH)

43:09.040 --> 43:11.000
..but...but... (SPEAKS IN SPANISH)

43:11.000 --> 43:13.360
(SHOUTS) Everybody calm down!

43:13.360 --> 43:14.800
(WOMAN YELLS IN SPANISH)
Hey!

43:14.800 --> 43:17.120
Hey! Hey! Hey!
Carlito!

43:17.120 --> 43:18.800
Carlito!
Calm down! Hey!

43:18.800 --> 43:20.160
Calmate!

43:20.160 --> 43:21.760
Hey, hey. Hey!
Carlito!

43:21.760 --> 43:23.360
You listen to my friend here, man!

43:23.360 --> 43:25.720
(SHOUTS) Yeah, he WAS listening!
Put that thing away!

43:25.720 --> 43:27.200
Carlito! Carlito!
Put it away!

43:27.200 --> 43:28.360
Carlito!

43:28.360 --> 43:31.560
(YELLS IN SPANISH)
Oh, oh, oh!

43:31.560 --> 43:33.400
(ALL YELL INDISTINCTLY)

43:33.400 --> 43:35.400
No. No. Relax!

43:35.400 --> 43:38.640
(ALL YELL INDISTINCTLY)
Everybody, calm down!

43:38.640 --> 43:39.880
Just relax!
(LAUGHS)

43:39.880 --> 43:42.400
Relax!
(ALL YELL INDISTINCTLY)

43:43.400 --> 43:44.720
(SILENCE)

43:49.000 --> 43:50.280
(LAUGHS)

43:50.280 --> 43:51.560
Yeah.

43:51.560 --> 43:54.960
OK, alright.
We're leaving, we're leaving.

43:54.960 --> 43:56.880
Gringos!

43:59.040 --> 44:03.000
(HOLLERS) Oh, my God!

44:03.000 --> 44:05.120
Holy shit,
I wonder what he's dreaming of?

44:05.120 --> 44:06.760
Hey, you alive back there, Bud?!

44:06.760 --> 44:08.240
Oh, mate!

44:09.240 --> 44:11.160
See, Newbie...

44:11.160 --> 44:12.880
..that's why I love you.

44:12.880 --> 44:16.040
You got balls of bloody steel...
(LAUGHS)

44:16.040 --> 44:17.920
..cool under pressure.

44:18.920 --> 44:20.880
Cool under pressure.

44:23.600 --> 44:27.480
You know, that's exactly what I was
looking for in a business partner.

44:28.480 --> 44:30.240
You're salty, mate.

44:30.240 --> 44:32.320
You're as salty as they come!

44:32.320 --> 44:33.800
(LAUGHS)
We're on!

44:34.800 --> 44:36.680
You mean it?! We're on?!

44:36.680 --> 44:39.680
Oh, baby, I mean it.
We're bloody on!

44:39.680 --> 44:41.560
We are on, baby!

44:41.560 --> 44:45.400
(FIRES MULTIPLE GUNSHOTS)
Whoo! Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

44:45.400 --> 44:46.600
(LAUGHS)

44:46.600 --> 44:47.760
Now...

44:47.760 --> 44:50.280
..eat the bloody worm, partner!

44:55.240 --> 44:58.160
Thanks, Dad.
Of course.

45:05.920 --> 45:08.880
I don't know
why he feels he's welcome here.

45:08.880 --> 45:11.720
It's a small town.
There's nowhere else to eat.

45:11.720 --> 45:14.600
Are you defending him too?
No, Dad.

45:15.920 --> 45:18.360
I don't know
why you stay in this place.

45:19.760 --> 45:20.840
(SIGHS)

45:20.840 --> 45:22.240
OK.

45:23.240 --> 45:24.960
Happy birthday, Tracy.

45:27.920 --> 45:30.040
Thank you for this.

45:30.040 --> 45:32.160
It was nice to see you, Dad.

45:39.440 --> 45:41.360
Scum!

46:11.680 --> 46:13.440
Where are all your mates?

46:14.760 --> 46:17.280
I could say the same to you.

46:19.080 --> 46:21.200
It's my birthday.

46:23.080 --> 46:24.720
I know.

46:28.400 --> 46:30.240
That's half-full.

46:30.240 --> 46:32.560
(CHUCKLES)

46:37.800 --> 46:40.560
I'm sorry
you're having such a shit night.

46:42.240 --> 46:44.520
Not as shit as my brother's.

46:46.000 --> 46:48.520
You enjoy making enemies, Snap?

46:49.680 --> 46:53.000
I certainly seem
to be getting some practice at it.

46:53.000 --> 46:55.760
Well, you should learn
to not shit in your own nest.

46:55.760 --> 46:57.760
It's Trotter that started that one.

46:58.760 --> 46:59.760
Oh, my gosh.

46:59.760 --> 47:02.480
You two stole all of my contacts

47:02.480 --> 47:05.040
and you went into business
without me.

47:06.040 --> 47:11.000
And YOU used the money
I gave you to marry that prick.

47:11.000 --> 47:12.680
He's not a prick.

47:12.680 --> 47:14.160
He's acting like one.

47:14.160 --> 47:15.760
That makes two of you.

47:15.760 --> 47:18.000
How would you like me to act?

47:20.600 --> 47:22.400
YOU dumped ME, remember?

47:22.400 --> 47:25.080
Because you were fucking around
the whole time.

47:25.080 --> 47:27.360
So, Trotter's the next best bet,
is he?

47:27.360 --> 47:29.520
Get over it, Snap.

47:30.680 --> 47:33.520
Trotter had the balls to ask me out,
and I liked him.

47:33.520 --> 47:36.240
Liked him so much I married him.

47:44.520 --> 47:46.720
What about Dimma?

47:46.720 --> 47:49.320
He's a good kid. (CLEARS THROAT)

47:49.320 --> 47:51.240
He was,

47:51.240 --> 47:53.560
until you took him
on one of your Bali runs.

47:53.560 --> 47:56.160
He had shit luck, that's all.

47:57.200 --> 48:00.120
Did you know
he was carrying the drugs?

48:04.960 --> 48:07.520
He's falling apart in there.

48:08.760 --> 48:11.720
His life's ruined.
I didn't know he was carrying.

48:11.720 --> 48:14.440
Oh, Snapper. (SCOFFS)

48:17.840 --> 48:19.000
Sure.

48:20.000 --> 48:22.640
Whatever gets you through the night.

48:33.480 --> 48:36.040
I didn't think it'd be like this.

48:40.760 --> 48:42.800
Like what?

48:42.800 --> 48:44.760
All of it.

49:30.320 --> 49:32.200
(KNOCK AT DOOR)

49:39.560 --> 49:43.200
(WIND GUSTS)

49:43.200 --> 49:44.800
Yes?

49:46.600 --> 49:50.120
Uh... I just wanted to say that...

49:51.520 --> 49:53.560
..you were right.

49:55.120 --> 49:56.840
About what?

49:56.840 --> 49:58.880
I fucked up.

49:59.880 --> 50:01.360
Everything.

50:01.360 --> 50:03.000
Uh...

50:03.000 --> 50:05.200
But especially with Dim.

50:08.160 --> 50:10.440
I never should've taken him.

50:10.440 --> 50:12.440
He looked up to you.

50:17.400 --> 50:18.920
I know.

50:20.320 --> 50:22.600
And I'm gonna make it up to him.

50:23.800 --> 50:25.400
I promise.

50:30.000 --> 50:31.920
You can try.

50:34.640 --> 50:36.120
(SNIFFLES)

50:40.880 --> 50:42.600
Can I come in?

50:49.160 --> 50:50.840
'Night, Snapper.

50:57.160 --> 50:58.680
Happy birthday.

51:15.320 --> 51:18.320
(WAVES CRASH)

51:23.840 --> 51:26.000
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

51:26.000 --> 51:27.280
CHOC: Hey, Miss?

51:40.680 --> 51:42.560
Well, Hunter knows the scene
over there,

51:42.560 --> 51:45.760
so better him taking our stuff
and speaking their language

51:45.760 --> 51:48.120
while we are building Australia.

51:48.120 --> 51:49.560
And Buddy?

51:49.560 --> 51:51.000
Buddy'll be the face.

51:51.000 --> 51:53.480
Turns out no-one's
that interested in this one.

51:53.480 --> 51:55.520
(BIRD SQUAWKS)

51:55.520 --> 51:58.680
Look...I know it didn't happen
the way I said it would,

51:58.680 --> 52:01.160
but it's going to, OK?

52:01.160 --> 52:04.400
I got a feel for it,
we know what we're doing,

52:04.400 --> 52:06.680
and that includes you.

52:07.960 --> 52:11.040
I haven't forgiven you
for not calling me on my birthday.

52:11.040 --> 52:12.560
You want me to describe the vomit

52:12.560 --> 52:14.840
on that Mexican phone again?
Mm-mm, mm-mm, mm-mm!

52:14.840 --> 52:17.000
I know you made that up, Trot,
because you know me.

52:17.000 --> 52:19.880
I didn't even ask. Um...
How was your night?

52:19.880 --> 52:22.720
What did you do? Who'd you see?

52:23.800 --> 52:26.120
Just Dad. Nothing special.

52:27.120 --> 52:29.600
Yeah?
Mm.

52:32.320 --> 52:33.840
We're gonna be rich.

52:33.840 --> 52:36.240
I told you.

52:54.760 --> 52:58.000
Yeah, I'm running a school here,
not a halfway house.

52:58.000 --> 52:59.680
TRACY: Dimma, stop!

52:59.680 --> 53:01.520
Was I the last guy you had sex with?

53:01.520 --> 53:03.200
Will you marry me?

53:03.200 --> 53:05.160
It's my engagement party!

53:05.160 --> 53:06.160
Boom!

53:06.160 --> 53:08.040
I got an audition with Joseph Deluca.

53:08.040 --> 53:09.640
Warren wants her in the picture.

53:09.640 --> 53:10.640
Hey, Bud.

53:10.640 --> 53:12.440
What's your PhD?

53:12.440 --> 53:14.560
Feminist separatism
and institutional misogyny.

53:14.560 --> 53:15.560
Eh?

53:15.560 --> 53:17.360
You owe me a US licence fee.

53:17.360 --> 53:20.280
We're in the middle of an important
meeting about this right now.

53:20.280 --> 53:22.760
We're expanding the business.
Into what?

53:22.760 --> 53:24.760
I have missed you, Trot.

